Is there a way to do an ad with out pixel or postdate?  I do not have access to change data on my programming on my website.

Hi Candis, if you don't have access to change data on your website for Pixel or Postback, you can still create ads without using these tracking methods. However, please note that using Pixel or Postback provides better insights into user behavior and conversion tracking. If you need more detailed guidance on creating ads without these methods, please refer to this article: [How to create your first ad](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17618196971149-How-to-create-your-first-ad).
You're welcome, Candis! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.
No problem at all! I'm glad I could help. Have a great day!
Hi, can you tell me if my ad Campaign ID:1896984029735342082 is running?

Hi there! Unfortunately, I don't have the capability to check the status of your ad campaign directly. However, you can check the status of your ad campaign by logging into your News Break Ad Manager account and navigating to the 'Campaigns' section. If you need further assistance, you can contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
You're welcome! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.
